# Peer OD daemon backends for nginx hash upstream (Phase 4).
# Written to /etc/nginx/teamver-design-od-daemon-peers.inc (NOT conf.d — bare
# `server` lines are valid only inside upstream { include ... }).
# Multi-node: render_od_daemon_peers_nginx.sh writes ALL cluster private IPs
# (sorted, including self) — identical on every EC2:
#   server 10.0.1.11:7456 max_fails=2 fail_timeout=10s;
#   server 10.0.1.12:7456 max_fails=2 fail_timeout=10s;
#
# Do NOT use 127.0.0.1 in hash ring — breaks userId sticky across ALB nginx hops.
